<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201027/bf3e4bb6ed4f4e16b25c0188c84bc453.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">《万壑松风山雨过》/孙佩杰</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201027/8edd3afbbb6d4289b0a33bbf4bb4d5f3.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">《仙阁云停望松泉》/孙佩杰</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201027/282f5e863b584c019448413ef8e183e9.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">《云台临瀑》/孙佩杰</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201027/9870097364d541f59a204c63dab4fc8a.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">《云悠松幽》/孙佩杰</span></img></p>
